(274, 1, '2015-07-20 05:34:41', '2015-07-20 05:34:41', 'Dalmia Advisory Services Pvt Ltd was established with an objective of providing financial planning and wealth management solution to investors. At DASPL, we are always committed towards continuously working with you in implementing your financial plan so that we can give our best to make your financial goal the best possible chance for success.\r\n\r\nOur foremost motive is to spread the knowledge of financial literacy amongst the people and try to incorporate the habit of investment and savings within them.\r\n<h3>MISSION STATEMENT</h3>\r\nâ€œWe all pass through this world once. Letâ€™s do our job with honesty, sincerity and integrity.â€\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #7e1312;"><strong>VISION</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To be appointed as your Personal Financial Advisor.</li>\r\n	<li>To assist you in reaching goal.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide unbiased advice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[table id=1 /]', 'About Us', 'Dalmia Advisory Services Pvt Ltd was established with an objective of providing financial planning and wealth management solution to investors...', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-20 05:34:41', '2015-07-20 05:34:41', '', 10, 'http://webphics.com/wordpress/wp_dalmiablog/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2015-07-20 05:46:26', '2015-07-20 05:46:26', 'There are various investment options available like Mutual Funds, Shares, Bonds, Savings Schemes, Fixed Deposits, etc. All these products have different risks and returns associated with them. In Mutual Funds alone, there are more than 40 companies with over 500 schemes.The same is the case with insurance products also, be it life or general.\r\n\r\nIt becomes very difficult for an innocent investor to choose the ideal investment / insurance product specially when the agents selling these products trying to justify their product to be the best. We at SBA feel that there is no â€œbestâ€ product, rather all these products are good. The best product is one which will help you to meet your investment objective. Product â€œAâ€ may be best for Mr. X and product â€œBâ€ may be best for Mr.Y based on their needs.\r\n\r\nHence, we at SBA do not sell any of these products, rather we sell â€œServiceâ€. The service to choose the product which will be best suited to you. We assist you in choosing the product based on your investment objective, risk appetite and financial goal. Not only this, we do monitor your investment regularly, making adjustments as necessary.\r\n\r\nOur four-step advisory process include the following:\r\n\r\nNeed Analysis: We analyze &amp; assess your investment objectives including your comfort level with various asset classes and to fulfill a short-term or a long-term goal. Asset Allocation: We determine an optimal mix of asset classes to meet your financial goals.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #7e1312;">Portfolio Construction :</span></strong> Based on that asset mix, we build a customized, diversified portfolio of various investment products.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #7e1312;"><strong>Ongoing Review :</strong></span> We monitor your portfolioâ€™s performance, making adjustments as necessary, while communicating with you regularly.', 'Why Choose Us', 'There are various investment options available like Mutual Funds, Shares, Bonds, Savings Schemes, Fixed Deposits, etc. All these products have different risks and returns associated with them. In Mutual Funds alone, there are more than 40 companies with over 500 schemes.The same is the case with insurance products also, be it life or general.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-20 05:46:26', '2015-07-20 05:46:26', '', 107, 'http://webphics.com/wordpress/wp_dalmiablog/107-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
